.@RandomBuzzers Spread the word on Twitter & Facebook! Order ur copy on my Facebook page: http://t.co/tK7yLCqV & tweet abt it w/ #Modelland
.@RandomBuzzers A book is even more fun to experience when you have friends to share it with. #Modelland
.@RandomBuzzers ...I love the magical quality. Its like a dream come to life! #Modelland
.@RandomBuzzers I love the wild & wacky new world complete with fashion, modeling & runways. #Modelland
.@RandomBuzzers She's Cinderellas nasty step-sisters with a touch of Regina George from Mean Girls. ;-) #Modelland
.@RandomBuzzers There are no rules to writing! Tweak your story as you go along and add in layers to make it special.
.@RandomBuzzers Once youve really thought out the story arc & put pen to paper it can be scary to step back from it & try to be objective.
.@RandomBuzzers I've learned a lot about myself through conceiving of, writing and then editing #Modelland.
.@RandomBuzzers ...Ready Player One by Ernest Cline, A Visit From the Goon Squad by Jennifer Egan, and The White Tiger by Aravind Adiga.
.@RandomBuzzers So many great reads! Some recent favs include The Book Thief by Markus Zusak, Devil in the White City by Erik Larson...
.@RandomBuzzers Loved S.E. Hinton's The Outsiders and Rumble Fish. You've got to respect a bold and gritty female author!
.@RandomBuzzers Are You There God, It's Me Margaret (a classic) and Forever (hot hot hot!) are two favorites.
.@RandomBuzzers The books of @judyblume have always been an inspiration. Judy talks TO young people and not at them.
.@RandomBuzzers People would recognize me @NYPL, but thanks to the library's quiet rule, I could hide in plain sight.
.@RandomBuzzers The number 7 refers to #Modelland's magical supermodels, the famous Intoxibellas and the greatest kind of Intoxibella.
.@RandomBuzzers Tookie has a nasty classmate named Zarpessa, but that's the least of her worries.
.@RandomBuzzers When you start to get attention, the haters come out!
.@RandomBuzzers Metopia, u ask? 1 of the lands in my fantasy wrld. From Bou-Big-Tique Nation2Digiridoo theyre a lil familiar but VRY strange
.@RandomBuzzers #Modelland is at the tip top of a foggy mountain in Metopia. The fog lifts 1 day per year: The Day of Discovery (T-DOD).
.@RandomBuzzers The male models of Bestosteronedouble as #Modelland's hunky handymen.
.@RandomBuzzers But of course dahling! #Modelland needs some eye candy and romance.
.@RandomBuzzers Lizzie's Tookie's BFF.The sight of her bright red hair always makes Tookie smile but she's a tormented girl w/ painful past.
.@RandomBuzzers Piper is SansColor's pale princess with bright pink eyes and a mind as sharp as they come. #Modelland
.@RandomBuzzers Shiraz from Canne Del Abra is 4'7" and may give a little 'tude at first, but her sour quickly turns to sweet. #Modelland
.@RandomBuzzers Dylan from Bou-Big-Tique Nation has curves that will give you whiplash and isn't afraid to speak her mind. #Modelland
.@RandomBuzzers Tookie is a little gangly, a lot awkward & ever-so Unfabulous just like I was, but she's got spark & is loyal 2 her friends.
.@RandomBuzzers So crazy that #Modelland is on shelves! I can't wait to hear what everyone thinks!
